name: Social Skatey Jumper
description:
Yo Dudes! Are you ready for the challenge of a lifetime?

Tap to make the vamp jump. Avoid the walls to level up and grab those trophies to bling Jumpy up!

- Pro Pimp Poncho
- Hip Hop Helmet
- Cherry On Top Mint Ice Cream
- Sickest Pro Skateboarder Trucks
- Pro Snorkel Goggles

...and more!

The amazing new Social Skatey Jumper is here.

Play on an iPod, iPhone or iPad.

Enjoy!
